title: Microsoft Office 2013 ProPlus English (x86/x64) July 10, 2018
description:
* Release Info

- Language: English (en-US)
- Channel: Volume License
- Version: 15.0.4569.1506
- Proofing Tools: English, French, Spanish
- Updated: July 10, 2018
- 64-bit version runs on 64-bit systems only
- OS: Windows 10/8.1/8,7 SP1 + Server/Server 2012 R2/2012/Server 2008 R2

* Bonus folder

- Previous versions uninstallers (Office 2010, 2007, 2003)
- KMSpico 10.2.0 + Microsoft Toolkit 2.6.4 Final
- Classic Menu for Office 9.25 (adds Office 2003 type toolbars and menus to Office 2013)
- Office Tab Enterprise 12.0.0.228 (adds tabs to Word, PowerPoint, and Excel documents)
- Disable/Restore 'Sign In' option in Office applications (reg file)
- Disable/Restore Office Telemetry (reg file)
- ShellNewHandler (easily remove New Microsoft_xxxx document from Windows Explorer context menu)
- Visual Studio for Office Runtime (required update)

* Installation

- Delete any previously installed version (recommended) using the provided uninstallers and reboot if required
- Mount / burn / extract ISO file
- Install Office components
- Activate using KMSpico (recommended) / Microsoft Toolkit
- Install Visual Studio for Office Runtime

* Optional

- Merge reg file Disable / Restore Office Telemetry (takes effect after rebooting your machine)
- Merge reg file Disable / Restore 'Sign In' option in Office applications (takes effect after rebooting your machine)
- Install Classic Menu for Office / Office Tab
- Run ShellNewHandler (easily remove New Microsoft_xxxx document from Windows Explorer context menu)
